tyle="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">2、安全性能大幅度提高</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">3、反弹蠕变小，连接更牢固</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">4、重量比铜少一半，安装更轻便</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">5、耐腐性更强，柔韧性强、弯曲性能好</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">6、抗拉延展性好、电气性能优越</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;"></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">我司发明专利</span></span></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476855975428.jpg" style="float:none;" title="2458292608_1584772477.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476855998688.jpg" style="float:none;" title="2458295501_1584772477.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476856011034.jpg" style="float:none;" title="2458980502_1584772477.jpg"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">铝合金电缆概述：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">但同国外铜资源国家相比仍有很大差距。铝资源储量约30亿吨，约占世界总量的12%，相比于铜资源储量要丰富得多。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">电力电缆以铝代铜的时代到了。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">铜的进口量居高不下，中国国内铜精矿的供应不到30%，超过70%的比例需要依赖进口，这远远高于中国铁矿石和石油的对外依存程度。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">铜价一升再升，2001年至今，铜价的累计涨幅已经超过了400%。据力拓方面介绍，中国铜精矿和废铜的进口分别比去年同期增长了26%和19%。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">铜矿产资源及矿产品的供需矛盾日益突出，在质量有所保证的基础上使用资源丰富、价格较低的铝合金电力电缆，顺应了国内建设资源节约社会的大趋势。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-seri;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; font-size: 12pt;">针对国际铜价高涨以及铜价不稳，加上中国的铜矿资源匮乏，面临枯竭的境遇，中国以铜导体为主的电线电缆行业的发展面临一个两难的选择。在这一背景下推广以铝合金为导体的电线电缆是一个极佳的时机</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">公司介绍</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"></span></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476856551750.jpg" style="float:none;" title="2454313838_1584772477.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476856601556.jpg" style="float:none;" title="2458295347_1584772477.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://lubanlucky.com/build_materials/Public/static/ueditor/php/upload/20151116/14476856748724.jpg" title="2458295347_1584772477.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋_gb2312;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><br/></span><br/></p>', '规格:6平方', '供应商:广东欣意铝合金电缆有限公司,品牌:欣意电缆,型号:zc-bhlv,用途:动力装置,横截面:6平方,额定电压:450/750V,芯数:单芯,执行标准:GB/UL/IEC,内置材质:聚氯乙烯绝缘,每卷长度:100米'),
