: 12pt;">柱</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;; font-size: 12pt;">可以准确快速地装配</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">6</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;; font-size: 12pt;">钢</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">柱</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;; font-size: 12pt;">可回收利用</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">二</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">钢柱用途：</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">钢柱按截面形式可分为实腹柱和格构柱<span style="font-family: arial;">.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实腹柱具有整体的截面，最常用的是工形截面；格构柱的截面分为两肢或多肢，各肢间用缀条或缀板联系，当荷载较大、柱身较宽时钢材用量较省。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;; font-size: 12pt;"><img alt="结构钢预制件  一般预制件 工业建筑预制件" src="http://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/668/545/2255545866_1413427588.jpg" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;" height="562" width="750"/><br class="img-brk"/></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">三 钢柱种类<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">;</span></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);"><img alt="结构钢预制件  一般预制件 工业建筑预制件" src="http://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/720/033/2259330027_1413427588.jpg" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;"/><br class="img-brk"/></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">1 H<span style="font-family: 宋体;">钢柱：包括（</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">HN ---HW --HM</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）焊接结构</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">H</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">钢。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">H<span style="font-family: 宋体;">型钢是由工字型钢优化发展而成的一种断面力学性能更为优良的经济型断面钢材，尤其断面与英文字母“</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">H</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”相同而得名。其特点如下：</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆翼缘宽，侧向刚度大。</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆抗弯能力强，比工字钢大约<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">5%-10%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆翼缘两表面相互平行使得连接、加工、安装简便。</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆ 与焊接工字钢相比，成本低，精度高，残余应力小，无需昂贵的焊接材料和焊缝检测，节约钢结构制作成本<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">30%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">左右。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆相同截面负荷下．热轧<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">H</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">钢结构比传统钢结构重量减轻</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">15%-20%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆与砼结构相比，热轧<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">H</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">钢结构可增大</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">6%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的使用面积，而结构自重减轻</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">20%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">30%</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，减少结构设计内力。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆<span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">H</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">型钢可加工成</span><span style="font-family: ;times new roman;;">T</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">型钢，蜂窝梁可经组合形成各种截面形式，极大满足工程设计与制作需求。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">应用范围：</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">H<span style="font-family: 宋体;">型钢主要用于工业与民用结构中的梁、柱构件。</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆工业构筑物的钢结构承重支架</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆地下工程的钢桩及支护结构</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆石油化工及电力等工业设备结构</span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;"> 大跨度钢桥构件</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆船舶、机械制造框架结构</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆火车、汽车、拖拉机大梁支架</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">◆港口传送带、高速挡板支架</span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br/></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">2<span style="font-family: 宋体;">钢箱形柱：</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img alt="结构钢预制件  一般预制件 工业建筑预制件" src="http://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/900/691/2257196009_1413427588.jpg" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;" height="560" width="750"/></span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">因为其形状如一个大的铁箱，因此而得名。一般钢结构上用作梁或者柱子。体的图纸会有所区别及变化。有的如“<span style="font-family: arial;">#</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”型，四边都出来的，也有的如“口”，当然也有半封口的。所以进行箱型柱的加工一定要有图纸，而且有的还要在柱里面加上一些筋板之类的。也有人用大的方矩管代替箱型柱的。但生产能力限制，往往厚度达不到要求的。大多数的箱型柱是指埋弧焊接的，三条缝中有一条要特殊焊接，难度会比较大</span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">。</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">3<span style="font-family: 宋体;">格构柱：</span></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);"><img alt="结构钢预制件  一般预制件 工业建筑预制件" src="http://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/708/545/2255545807_1413427588.jpg" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;"/></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;"> 格构柱：属于压弯构件，多用于厂房框架柱和独立柱，优点在于很好的节约材料；截面一般为型钢或钢板设计成双轴对称或单轴对称的截面。</span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br/></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">格构体系构件由肢件和缀材组成。格构柱可能是主要的应用形式，有缀条柱和缀板柱。格构柱的主要思想是：将材料面积向距离惯性轴远的地方布置，能保证相同轴向抗力条件下增强构件抗弯性能，并且节省材料。</span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><br/></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">4<span style="font-family: 宋体;">十字钢柱：</span></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);"><img alt="重型结构钢构件 管桩基础构件" src="http://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2015/851/665/2255566158_1413427588.jpg" style="border: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;"/><br class="img-brk"/></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">其受弯承载力、延性及抗</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">震承载力较好，但与圆管柱、箱型柱比，其抗扭性能较差，特别是在高轴压比下</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">变形很快，故一般与钢筋混凝土组合形成型钢混凝土组合柱受力性能更好。</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ;Hiragino Sans GB;, Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; fon