-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">～1.900.1kg/L（A＋B组份，23℃）</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">流挂性能在立面最大厚度达15mm时无流挂（依据EN1799标准）</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">单层施工厚度单层最大到30mm，当分层施工时，为了防止减少可施工时间，在一层材料用完后，再进行下一层材料的搅拌混合。</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">体积变化收缩：固化后无收缩</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">热膨胀系数59×10－6/℃（温度范围：23℃-60℃），依据EN1770标准</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">热稳定性热变形温度＝49℃7天23℃时，依据ISO75标准，材料厚度在10mm</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">物理性质　</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"><strong style="font-weight: 700;">抗压强度　</strong></span></p><p class="p" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: